org.apache.paimon.partition

Interface PartitionPredicate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PartitionPredicate.DefaultPartitionPredicate, PartitionPredicate.MultiplePartitionPredicate

    public interface PartitionPredicate
    A special predicate to filter partition only, just like Predicate.
